Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.13,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Siapa dia tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.50,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Pelajar pindah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.24,0:02:33.50,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Mulai hari ini, pelajar pindahan baharu akan\Nmenyertai kelas kita, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:32.28,Atas,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Sebelum ni tak pernah nampak pun dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.34,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu semua berbaiklah dengan dia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.60,Atas,Pelajar A,0,0,0,,Jadi dialah pelajar pindahan dari setinggan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:37.15,Utama,Pelajar B,0,0,0,,Setinggan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:40.97,Utama,Pelajar B,0,0,0,,Seseorang sehina dia\Nmenyertai Akademi Diraja kita?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.58,Utama,Pelajar C,0,0,0,,Khabarnya dia menyelamatkan Puteri Flora,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.50,Utama,Pelajar C,0,0,0,,jadi Yang Mulia Raja,\Nmemperkenankan kemasukkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:51.27,Condong,Philip III,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kerja yang bagus menyelamatkan\Nputeriku. Beta berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.07,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Kalam tuanku, patik berbesar hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.84,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Dengan merendah diri dan hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:56.15,Condong,Philip III,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.99,Condong,Philip III,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sebagai ganjaran,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:02.37,Condong,Philip III,0,0,0,,{\blur4}beta menganugerahkan kamu untuk\Nmemasuki Akademi Diraja beserta biasiswa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.10,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.61,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Perkenalkan diri kamu pada semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.31,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:09.91,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Nama saya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.92,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Atas kurniaan baginda ke atas saya,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.86,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,saya telah dibenarkan untuk belajar di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.66,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya mungkin banyak kekurangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.37,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,selamat berkenalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.13,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.30,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Sekurangnya dia boleh cakap macam hamba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.55,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baiklah Rio, kamu boleh duduk di sana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.20,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:42.22,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baiklah semua, mari kita mulakan kelas kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.01,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Hari ini kita belajar sungguh-sungguh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.16,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Baik..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:51.05,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,210)}Buka buku nota kamu dan salin semula formula ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.62,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baiklah, kamu semua cuba selesaikan\Nsoalan ini dengan sendiri.{woi masuk2 terus cam exam ke :kekw:}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.91,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Baik, cikgu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.66,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Senang je ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:06.79,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.99,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu tak perlu paksa diri kamu ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.81,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik, terima kasih kerana\Nambil berat pada saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.77,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Mesti dia langsung tak boleh baca. {bro, I'll be flexing writing in jp in that world}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.90,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Dah, dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.96,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu semua. Tumpu pada soalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.69,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Mana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:33.25,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Terdapat petunjuk tersembunyi di\Nkertas itu! Mana perginya ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:31.14,Atas,Rio,0,0,0,,Sini ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:33.25,Atas,Rio,0,0,0,,Profesor Celia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.33,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fs71}Aduhai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.26,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu tak boleh baca tanda ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.88,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.37,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya tak boleh membaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.02,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.53,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya datang untuk kelas persendirian...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:51.64,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, ya! Baguslah kamu datang.\NSaya dah lama menunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.79,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Dia lupa, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.63,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,K-Kalau begitu,\Njemputlah masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.61,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:04:59.90,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Maaf mengganggu—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:05.97,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Buat masa sekarang, agak bersepah sedikit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.86,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ha...{asian ha}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.99,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Biasanya lebih kemas dan teratur, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:14.39,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Sekejap ya. Saya nak buat sedikit ruang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:17.12,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terdapat banyak buku yang\Nnampak susah di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi Profesor nampak sangat muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.31,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh, tu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.53,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Saya masih baru dua belas tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.49,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.56,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Sepatutnya saya masuk sekolah rendah,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.76,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,tapi saya lompat kelas dan\Nlulus sekolah menengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.60,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kamu mesti pintar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.49,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,B-Boleh la...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.90,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya dah siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.33,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,S-Siap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.82,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Eh? Hebatnya!\NSemua jawaban kamu betul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.45,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Bahkan kamu mencongak dengan laju...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.28,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Itu hanyalah pendaraban dan\Npembahagian mudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.15,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Asalkan saya tahu angka dan simbolnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.27,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Mudah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.83,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Di dalam kelas kamu, yang boleh\Njawab paling kurang Christina-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.33,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh? B-Betulkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.13,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Masuk akal juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.76,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.30,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,dulunya pelajar universiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.28,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.30,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Dari mana kamu belajar ilmu hisab?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.38,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dari arwah ibu saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.53,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.27,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Boleh tahan berilmu juga ibu kamu, ya? {kyoyonoaru 教養のある}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.27,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.49,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dia seorang yang baik dan peramah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.42,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Maaf ya, saya buat kamu terkenang akan beliau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.40,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh, tak mengapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.86,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baguslah. Saya buat teh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.08,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Silakan minum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.01,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:46.59,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sedapnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:49.64,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baguslah!\NBila kamu minum secawan teh sedap...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.62,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Terasa seperti sedang bahagia, kan?
Comment: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.62,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,...تراس سڤرتي سدڠ بهاݢيا کن
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.55,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.23,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.53,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dengan hari pertama kamu di akademi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.65,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kalau ada apa-apa masalah,\Nboleh beritahu saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:06.19,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ta—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.07,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.26,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Yakah... Kalau ada apa-apa—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.75,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, satu benda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.74,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Apa dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:20.21,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Boleh kamu sarankan saya\Nbeberapa buku kanak-kanak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.92,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Buku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.99,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya mahu belajar membaca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.38,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh... Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.43,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Saya akan pilih dari perpustakan untuk kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.11,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:29.72,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,{\iclip(750,906,1312,1031)}Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:30.72,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,{\iclip(865,916,1378,1026)}Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:31.63,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,{\iclip(990,893,1353,1028)}Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.51,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,{\iclip(1171,896,1363,1028)}Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.47,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:34.47,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Satu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.56,Atas,ParaPelajar; background,0,0,0,,Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.47,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Dua!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.43,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Tiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.56,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Empat! Lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.56,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Tangkas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:43.33,Atas,ParaPelajar; background,0,0,0,,Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:43.61,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.56,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Y-Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:49.32,Atas,ParaPelajar; background,0,0,0,,Satu, dua, tiga, empat, lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.26,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Seranglah saya dari arah mana yang kamu suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.07,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.32,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.23,Atas,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Kekuda apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.16,Atas,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Kekuda yang pelik...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.75,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Baik, datanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.62,Condong,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Baiklah, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.29,Condong,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Ayuh, serang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.01,Condong,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Jangan teragak-agak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.88,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Kemahiran pedang yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.51,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.66,Condong,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.94,Condong,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Jangan mengelak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.37,Condong,Atuk Haruto,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Majulah terus ke dada lawan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:38.71,Roana,Roana,0,0,0,,Daripada mengelak ke luar,\Ndia terus menuju ke pihak lawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.83,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Teknik dia langsung tak betul. {ppfff looks whos talking}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.05,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Macam sampah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.33,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Baiklah. Sampai sini sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:52.16,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Rio, kamu ada gaya untuk menjadi seorang satria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.55,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Mohon maaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.93,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,saya tak berminat untuk menyertai kesateria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:56.83,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.18,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas kata-kata tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.26,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Apa? {ppfff dengki ckp bodo :kekw:}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.47,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Apa yang dia cakap tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.22,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Giler ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:06.60,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.23,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.24,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Selepas sekolah pun kamu belajar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.94,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sebab ujian akhir sudah pun hampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:16.58,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu baru sahaja masuk ke sini. Tak perlulah\Nkamu terlalu risaukan markah kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:17.49,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.99,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi, saya akan buat yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.34,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baguslah begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.77,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Semua orang dah dapat kertas ujian?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.18,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Dah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.38,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Baiklah, mula!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:31.00,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Aduh! Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:32.69,Atas,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Satu, dua, tiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.11,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Dah... Tutup mulut!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.13,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kalian semua, buat yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.15,Condong,Haruto,0,0,0,,Mii...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:09:58.36,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,...chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.85,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Itu dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:01.66,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Dia ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.42,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Biar betul?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.44,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Budak setinggan\Nbaru masuk ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.65,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Raja mesti buang tabiat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.70,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ayase Miharu adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.24,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,sahabat semasa Amakawa Haruto kecil .
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:19.92,Condong,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi, bila ibu bapa Haruto bercerai,\Nmereka berdua terpisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:24.33,Haruto,Haruto,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kemudian, saya nampak Mii-chan\Nsemula di sekolah menengah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:25.87,Haruto,Haruto,0,0,0,,{\i1}dan itu sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.25,Haruto,Haruto,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dia tidak lagi kembali ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.65,Haruto,Haruto,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seperti dirinya habis dipadam dari pandangan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.65,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dah tu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.15,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Amakawa Haruto dah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.92,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sekarang, aku adalah Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.09,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Bukannya Amakawa Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:44.97,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Sebab itulah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.94,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku akan teruskan hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.97,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Aku akan jadi kuat dan gagah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.89,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Mustahil lah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.80,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Biar betik?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.63,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.88,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Nani??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.38,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Seri dengan Christina-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.40,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Mustahil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.85,Utama,Roana,0,0,0,,Saya tempat ketiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.13,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Jangan nak mengarut!\NPasti ini kesilapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:02.59,Utama,Pelajar A,0,0,0,,Betul, betul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.18,Utama,Pelajar A,0,0,0,,Oi, dia dah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.57,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Kau! Kau meniru, kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.39,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa maksud kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.39,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.85,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Budak setinggan macam kau ni
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:14.22,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,mustahil boleh seri tempat pertama\Ndengan Christina-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.65,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Mustahil kau tak meniru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.53,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tempat pertama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:19.40,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Mesti kau pakai helah kotor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:22.20,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya ambil ujian seperti biasa sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.10,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Tipu ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.52,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Hentikan, Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.87,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Dengki seorang lelaki memalukan, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.45,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,A-Aku tak akan biarkan!\NAku akan—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.69,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Kamu ada bukti yang kukuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:36.50,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.35,Flora,Christina,0,0,0,,Fitnah tanpa saksi hanya akan\Nmencemarkan nama akademi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.09,Atas,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Tapi—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:45.22,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Pencapaian Rio kali ini\Nadalah atas hasil usahanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.41,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Saya boleh mengesahkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.35,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Profesor Celia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.26,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Aku tak terima perkara ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.79,Utama,Pelajar A,0,0,0,,Jom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:54.86,Utama,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.20,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih bany—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:12:00.27,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Tak apa. Saya bukan masuk campur untuk kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.30,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.60,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Lepas ni saya tak akan kalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.55,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.82,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tahniah kerana mendapat tempat pertama\Ndalam ujian akhir tahun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.13,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.76,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya kan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.23,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Saya risau sikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.09,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Risau?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:16.63,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.63,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Bila saya fikir akan ada ramai lagi\Npelajar yang cuba mencari kesalahan kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.88,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak mengapa, saya dah biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:24.63,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Alahai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.85,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Perundungan oleh bangsawan\Nitu perbuatan teruk, tahu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:33.14,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Katanya Profesor Celia pintar juga.\NAda perkara yang sama terjadi pada kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:38.73,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Adalah juga sekian-sekian dari orang\Nyang tinggi pangkat dan pengikutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.23,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tapi saya tak layan pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.42,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dah agak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:44.27,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,T-Tapi saya ada kawan, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.42,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, saya juga takkan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.61,Celia,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya ada kamu, Profesor Celia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.58,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ah, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.08,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.72,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu mainkan saya ke?\NAnggap saya macam budak pula!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.35,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi Profesor kan lebih tua dari saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:09.19,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,B-Betul tu... Maksudnya... Kamu\Nanggap saya sebagai kawan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:09.95,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.26,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak boleh ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.15,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Bukan tak boleh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:14.56,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.56,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Bukan... Tak boleh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.55,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Boleh kamu ulang lagi sekali?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.57,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Saya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.82,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Saya cakap saya tak kisah!\NTerukla kamu ni Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.12,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tengoklah suasana sikit, ishh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.09,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:35.08,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dikala saya susah, bantulah saya\Nsebagai guru dan kawan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.58,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,B-Boleh je!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:42.95,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kalau Rio menangis kerana dirundung nanti,\Nsaya akan berikan kamu dakapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:47.47,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Badan Profesor Celia kecil jadi\Nnampak sesuai untuk berpaut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.86,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Mana ada kecil! Saya dalam tumbesaran, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.74,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh, cukup-cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.03,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.46,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Alahai Rio ni!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:06.99,Era_Masa,teks,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,909.022)}Tahun 966 Era Suci
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:06.95,Atas,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Pertandingan kesatria diraja akan\Ndiadakan lagi pada tahun ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:11.56,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Wakil untuk bahagian sekolah rendah\Ntelah pun dipilih dari kelas ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.95,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Jika nama kamu di sebut, maju ke hadapan!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.83,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Tahun enam, Alphonse Rodan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.89,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:20.30,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Tahun lima, Stewart Huguenot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:20.92,Utama,Stewart,0,0,0,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:23.64,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:24.85,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.84,Atas,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Eh? Biar betul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.78,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.84,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.84,Atas,ParaPelajar,0,0,0,,Dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.99,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Tunggu sekejap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.08,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.56,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Saya tak boleh terima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:38.13,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Seseorang yang sangat hina ini terpilih\Nuntuk menyertai pertandingan kesatria...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.45,Atas,ParaPelajar; background,0,0,0,,Betul, betul!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.84,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,sangat memalukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.03,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Lagipun, dia tak boleh guna sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.73,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Ini sudah ditetapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.45,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Muktamad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.40,Atas,ParaPelajar; background,0,0,0,,Tapi kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.16,Atas,ParaPelajar; background,0,0,0,,Aku tak boleh terima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.58,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Khabarnya kamu akan menyertai pertandingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.47,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya, begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.30,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kalau kamu berjaya dalam pertadingan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:05.56,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,kesatria mungkin akan melantik\Nkamu sebelum tamat sekolah... tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.52,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi saya tak berniat langsung\Nuntuk menyertai kesatria. {sheeshhhh}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.51,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.30,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.16,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu dah semakin tinggi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.78,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.15,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Sudah lima tahun berlalu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.86,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Profesor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:21.85,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.10,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Dari dulu lagi kamu ni kecil je kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.20,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Mana ada "kecil"!\NSaya dalam tumbesaran, tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.97,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Lima tahun dulu pun kamu kata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.38,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fnOpen Sans Semibold}( `ε´ )
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.86,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Teh akan sejuk, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.86,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.72,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Aroma yang harum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.96,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Sedapnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.29,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Walaupun daun tehnya sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:44.79,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,tapi bila Rio buat teh, baunya sangat berbeza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.42,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya hanya ikut arahan\Ndari buku yang saya baca.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.33,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu kata kamu tak mahu menyertai kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.05,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Jadi apa yang kamu akan buat\Nselepas mendapat ijazah nanti?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.65,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya rasa mahu mengembara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.62,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.40,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ada satu tempat yang saya mahu pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:16:00.62,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Jadi... kamu bercadang untuk\Nmeninggalkan negara ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.87,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Negara ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.69,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,susah untuk saya tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.28,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ada betulnya, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.53,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Apa kata kamu kerja di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.11,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.80,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kalau Rio tiada nanti,\Napa pun tak menjadi nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.12,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak adalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.31,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tengok ni! Cara kamu mengemas di sini...\NSangat bersih!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.33,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Dan kamu pun buat teh yang sedap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:25.63,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu selalu menegur saya\Nketika saya sibuk mengkaji... Dan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.59,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya berterima kasih di atas\Nkeprihatinan Profesor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.25,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tapi Profesor pun, tak lama lagi\Nakan masuk fasa perkahwinan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.86,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kenapa tiba-tiba ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:36.88,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak eloklah kalau ada orang luar\Nberada di makmal kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.89,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Tapi saya bukan mahu berkahwin pun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:44.02,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Apa pun, saya rasa Profesor\Nbebas buat apa sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:47.26,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ha! Mesti kamu ingat saya\Ntak akan sempat berkahwin, kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:51.94,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Profesor Celia muda dan manis,\Nsaya yakin kamu tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:55.84,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kamu cakap seperti saya ini budak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.58,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tak lah. Kamu seorang wanita yang menawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.33,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Jangan usik saya macam tu la...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.06,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:07.58,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Ah! Err, tu... Kemana tempat\Nyang Rio mahu pergi tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.54,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tanah air ibu bapa saya, wilayah Yagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:15.09,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Yagumo? Tempat di seberang belantara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:17.67,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,253)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:24.73,Haruto,Ayame,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Bila kamu dah besar nanti, ibu akan bawa\Nkamu ke sana. Tempat bernama Yagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.23,Haruto,Rio; 5 yo,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur4}Betul? Janji, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:28.97,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,{\fad(247,0)}Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.53,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,T-Tapi buat masa ini\Nhanyalah perancangan sahaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.74,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:40.85,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Sekarang, pertandingan di antara kesatria diraja
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.79,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,dan pelajar dari Akademi Diraja akan dimulakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:51.17,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Dengan ini, saya, Alfred Emerle,\Nakan menjadi juri pada hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.42,Atas,Kayangan,0,0,0,,Segak sentiasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:55.42,Utama,Pompuan,0,0,0,,Emerle-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:18:00.43,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Sekolah Rendah Akademi Diraja Beltrum!\NPencabarnya, Rio, maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.81,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Hoi! Jangan buat benda memalukan pula.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.26,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Kau akan merendahkan\Npadangan orang pada aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:13.32,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya akan cuba untuk\Ntidak melakukan pertandingan buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.44,Utama,Alphonse,0,0,0,,Takde sape mengharapkan pape dari kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:20.74,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:22.49,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Buat yang terbaik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.85,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya bersedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.75,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.50,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Dan dari Kesatria Diraja,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.50,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,pencabarnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.72,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Charles Arbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.81,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Aku tahu kau daftar di akademi ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.38,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,tapi tak sangka pula budak jijik yang dulu tu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.80,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,akan jadi lawan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.43,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Saya terhutang budi di atas jagaan kamu dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:50.00,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Maafkan saya kerana tak banyak membantu dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.61,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Berhenti bercakap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:55.10,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Bersedia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.83,Condong,Emerle,0,0,0,,Kekuda apa ni?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.00,Condong,Charles,0,0,0,,Langsung tak ada perisai, nganjing ke apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.91,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Mula!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.08,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Hebatnya Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.59,Roana,Roanna,0,0,0,,Dengan tenang dia menepis serangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:18.88,Condong,Charles,0,0,0,,Disebabkan kau, aku dilucutkan\Npangkat lima tahun lepas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:21.47,Condong,Charles,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan lupakan penghinaan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.22,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,K-Kejap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.14,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Kenapa pula kesatria berlawan\Nbetul-betul dengan pelajar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.34,Utama,Pengajar,0,0,0,,Sekarang, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:29.93,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.02,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Inilah penamat kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:40.20,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Sampai situ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:43.27,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Pemenangnya adalah, wakil akademi, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:44.99,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,T-Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.18,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Saya terleka je tadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.05,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:49.82,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Selepas ini saya akan—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.08,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Bodoh ke apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.58,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Kalah tetap kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.73,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Alfred...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.94,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.30,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Kalau kau ahli Kesatria Diraja,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.31,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,kau akan terima kekalahan dan pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.77,0:20:06.47,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,A-Aku mengalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.55,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas perlawanannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.23,Utama,Emerle,0,0,0,,Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.03,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Sugoi! Sugoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.24,Condong,Emerle,0,0,0,,Rio, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.49,Condong,Emerle,0,0,0,,Aku menantikan masa depannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.79,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Tak guna punya budak!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.37,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Kalau aku sungguh-sungguh\Ntadi, boleh menang dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:39.30,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Dalam keadaan begitu, apa salahnya\Nbiarkan pelajar yang menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.13,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Jika diikutkan keadaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:45.21,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,akhirnya kesemua kesatria juga yang menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.14,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Alahai, kebudak-budakan betullah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.41,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,K-Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.52,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Aku cuma bagi dia menang je!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.82,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Duta Empayar Proxia memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.17,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Sangat memahami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.45,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Dan... Pelajar yang bertarung dengan kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.16,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.57,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Tak dinafikan, dia mempunyai\Ngerakan yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.72,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Budak tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.61,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Lima tahu lepas,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:10.37,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,dia disyaki terlibat dalam\Nkes penculikan Puteri Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.87,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Masa itu, aku menyoal siasatnya dengan kasar...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.17,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,Kesudahannya, dia tak cakap apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:17.88,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.71,Utama,Reiss,0,0,0,,Nampaknya kamu berdua\Nditakdikan berjumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.36,Utama,Charles,0,0,0,,{\fs70}Takdir ke mendenyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:28.35,Condong,Reiss,0,0,0,,Begitu... Pada masa itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:36.23,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Harapnya cepatlah dia keluar...\NSaya kenalah raikan kemenangan dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:37.48,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:43.11,Celia,Celia,0,0,0,,Dia mahu pergi ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.30,Utama,younger female student,0,0,0,,I-Ini. Tolonglah baca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.46,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:53.48,Utama,younger female student,0,0,0,,P-Pertandingan semalam!\NAwak memang... sangat hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:56.66,Utama,younger female student,0,0,0,,Sangat gagah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:57.90,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Ah! Kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:21:59.98,Utama,Rio,0,0,0,,Tunggu sekejap!
